CatDescriptText: David L. Lawrence was Mayor of the City of Pittsburgh 1946-1959, Governor of Pennsylvania 1959-1963, and he died in 1966.
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of three women and four men, including Pittsburgh Mayor David L. Lawrence signing document, and Rev. Charles Foggie standing on right, gathered in the Office of the Mayor at the City County Building
